" Run this in tridactyl to read the configuration: `source --url <raw-text-url>`

sanitise tridactyllocal tridactylsync

unbind <<
unbind >>
unbind <C-f>
set theme dark
bind j scrollline 4
bind k scrollline -4
bind J tabnext
bind K tabprev
set hintfiltermode vimperator-reflow
set hintnames numeric


" Comment toggler for Reddit, Hacker News and Lobste.rs
bind ;c hint -Jc [class*="expand"],[class="togg"],[class="comment_folder"]


" Only hint search results on Google and DDG
bindurl www.google.com f hint -Jc .rc > div > a
bindurl www.google.com F hint -Jbc .rc > div > a
bindurl ^https://lite.duckduckgo.com/lite f hint -Jc [class=result-link]
bindurl ^https://lite.duckduckgo.com/lite F hint -Jbc [class=result-link]
